<item>
            <title>[LU-2465] e2mmpstatus utility</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2465</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is a utility to read MMP status. This is based on dump_mmp() in debugfs.c.&lt;br/&gt;
We added checking recent MMP updates and printed out updated nodename.&lt;br/&gt;
This helps the lustre does failover. It prevents both servers issue STONITH at same time when the heartbeat&apos;s interlink connection lost. It&apos;s kind of idea of quorum disk for the HA clustering. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Lustre, failover, pacemaker/corosync</environment>
        <key id="16896">LU-2465</key>
