                            <comment id="233102" author="adilger" created="Thu, 6 Sep 2018 09:53:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The mmpstatus utility was landed into the upstream e2fsprogs in commit 32b8802aa5d867a0497cd6135c5f48039b0ba71c for the 1.44.3 release.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note that the utility also accepts the &quot;e2mmpstatus&quot; name, so in new deployments it would be better to use &quot;e2mmpstatus&quot; since this makes it more clear that it is part of e2fsprogs.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
